lead_paragraph: Half-centuries by Virat Kohli, Cheteshwar Pujara and Ravichandran Ashwin kept India on course for a first innings lead after England made a spirited comeback on day two of the third test on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: India Set for First Innings Lead After England Fightback
